\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 5. Power Analysis\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Stata solves for parameters using the 
\f0\b non-central F distribution
\f1\b0 .\
