\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 
\f0\b Variance (Standard):
\f1\b0  $V(\\hat\{\\beta\}) = s^2 (X'X)^\{-1\}$ where $s^2$ is Mean Squared Error
