\fs24 \nosupersub .\uc0\u8232 \u8232 \
\ls12\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 
\f0\b Cluster (vce(cluster id)):
\f1\b0  Sums residuals over clusters $j$ instead of individuals $i$, adjusting for intragroup correlation
